value.0: A well dressed Cambion, running the emporium's shop

Helms such as these have only recently begun to surface in the region, however they look ancient. Relics of an old war, long forgotten and a time nearly lost, these powerful artifacts were likely worn by the champions or paragons of the people that created them.

While the original creators of these helms seem to remain unknown, they do bare an uncanny resemblance to the natives of the Mylock Hills.
